{"tid":736851,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"香港youtube觀眾新不如舊","createTime":"2018-07-10T14:04:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-10T14:14:24.000Z","uid":12618,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9907bd18d9f6ded7124444ee5288877605d1fb8b","tid":736851,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T14:04:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_TlhJLnJW9I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_TlhJLnJW9I&d=eR1TBwj6C9DhNxCubXnTRv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=a51de913\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_TlhJLnJW9I</a><br />\n<br />\n攞司徒夾帶既偷食總司令做例子<br />\n條片係2012年既 離而家係6年前<br />\n<br />\n條片係煮公仔麵<br />\n條片係有教學性質但以輕鬆為主 <br />\n其中都有好多時間去串下cooking hayhay<br />\n但攞cooking hayhay黎串都只係效果<br />\n果陣時我地做觀眾都知係笑下而並非真心起晒鋼串<br />\n<br />\n睇返下面啲近年留言 特別係近兩三年<br />\n屌你老味一大堆小學雞<br />\n又屌佢搞咁多野多舊魚<br />\n呢樣唔啱果樣唔啱<br />\n叫人唔好做自己又走去做<br />\n屌你老味知唔知咩係搞笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁認真做乜撚<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/10/220253_f1d96e56bd9f8ce6643021d52d633227.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F10%2F220253_f1d96e56bd9f8ce6643021d52d633227.png&h=8906a36f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/10/220300_b1f405f47958f2039c3fe09927ce70eb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F10%2F220300_b1f405f47958f2039c3fe09927ce70eb.png&h=012b7f13&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/10/220307_5bff7b088050a93825a869c0032cfb2d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F10%2F220307_5bff7b088050a93825a869c0032cfb2d.png&h=aafa6eca&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9e2f21e8f4a9b82a24b00ad299de989ec6134e4e","tid":736851,"uid":188,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"rep